  ${
    $d J m n u $.  $d X m n u $.  $d Y m n u $.
    tlmconst.1 $e |- X = U. J $.
    $( A constant sequence converges to the constant. $)
    tlmconst $p |- ( ( J e. Top /\ Y e. X ) ->
                                    ( NN X. { Y } ) ( ~~>t ` J ) Y ) $=
      ( vm vu vn ctop wcel wa cn csn cxp ctlm cfv wbr wf cv cuz wral wrex cnei
      w3a wss fconstg snssi fss syl11anc adantl simpr c1 1nn elnnuz wceq
      fvconst2g adantll adantlr ssnei snssg biimpar syldan adantr eqeltrd
      sylan2br r19.21aiva fveq2 raleqdv rcla4ev sylancr 3jca tlmbr mpbird ) AHI
